item.title: CVE-2020-5384|2024-08-04T08:30:24.008Z -- dell -- rsa%20authentication%20agent%20for%20microsoft%20windows
item.description: Authentication Bypass Vulnerability RSA MFA Agent 2.0 for Microsoft Windows contains an Authentication Bypass vulnerability. A local unauthenticated attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability by using an alternate path to bypass authentication in order to gain full access to the system.
